  "events": [
    {
      "id": "action_network:87d3453f-d80d-4459-969b-ab04792dba3f",
      "name": "Coffee with Comrades: to your Healthcare!",
      "date": "2026-05-16T15:00:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "3:00 PM, Saturday May 16, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-05",
      "month_label": "May 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p>Meet DSA Healthcare Working Group comrades and join fellow activists chilling after Darializa canvass in this awesome spot on Amsterdam right by 125. Let's go Darializa, let's go New York Health Act. </p><p><br></p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/coffee-with-comrades-to-you-healthcare",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/coffee-with-comrades-to-you-healthcare",
      "location": "1351 Amsterdam Ave",
      "borough": "New York"
    },
    {
      "id": "action_network:04ed8865-a68a-4980-9efb-13adbb3a526d",
      "name": "Healthcare Working Group May General Meeting",
      "date": "2026-05-21T19:00:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "7:00 PM, Thursday May 21, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-05",
      "month_label": "May 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p>Get plugged into the healthcare working group at our May General Meeting at the Peoiple's Forum.</p><p>This month we will share updates of the work we are doing and break-out to plan our action packed \"Hot Healthcare Summer\", building up to the Labor Day parade.</p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/healthcare-working-group-may-general-meeting-2",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/healthcare-working-group-may-general-meeting-2",
      "location": "320 W 37th St",
      "borough": "New York"
    },
    {
      "id": "action_network:ee9e4cd9-1262-4fd1-b97e-08c67c771f32",
      "name": "DSAcro",
      "date": "2026-05-24T17:00:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "5:00 PM, Sunday May 24, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-05",
      "month_label": "May 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p>\"Health is a state of complete physical, mental and social well-being and not merely the absence of disease\"</p><p>Invert your body and class society</p><p>Strengthen your core, build the base</p><p>Put the phone down and join a fun, safe, beginner-level acro-yoga class (with a touch of political education). </p><p>\"Acro-yoga\" is a playful practice with cooperative group stretching and poses that build trust, communication, strength and balance. Touching and lifting up your comrades encouraged but not necessary, nor is a partner. All body types and fitness levels welcome. Wear comfortable clothes.</p><p>A fundraiser for the DSA healthcare working group. Cost should not be a barrier, contact us if it is.</p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/dsacro",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/dsacro",
      "location": "669 Meeker Ave",
      "borough": "Brooklyn"
    },
    {
      "id": "action_network:97494210-b384-41f4-b47d-d9e3bdae5989",
      "name": "Sumud film screening",
      "date": "2026-05-24T19:00:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "7:00 PM, Sunday May 24, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-05",
      "month_label": "May 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p>We are screening the short film Sumud - we'll order food from Pita Palace and discuss as a group after</p><p>See the trailer</p><p>https://palestineexceptionfilm.com/sumud/</p><p>The film follows an American anesthesiologist volunteering at Nasser Hospital in Gaza as he works with Palestinian surgical teams that continue training even as the medical center is under siege</p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/sumud-film-screening",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/sumud-film-screening",
      "location": "669 Meeker Ave",
      "borough": "Brooklyn"
    }
  ],
